## v1.0.0 (2026-05-31)

**Initial version.** Turn red CI green on 22 fully-auto PRs across 7 HomericIntelligence
repos using purely mechanical autofixes with signed commits. Covered: shallow-clone
refspec trap, multi-PR shared-doc fan-out, markdownlint-cli2 `--fix` incompleteness
(MD013/MD007/MD031/MD032/MD034), single-hook pre-commit, re-signing pushed unsigned
commits, `gh pr checks` staleness vs check-runs API, aeolus noreply email requirement.
